com.samskivert.annotation
Annotation Type ReplacedBy

@Documented
@Inherited
@Retention(value=SOURCE)
@Target(value={TYPE,METHOD,FIELD})
public @interface ReplacedBy

An annotation for indicating that something has a preferred implementation elsewhere, without going so far as to deprecate it.

Required Element Summary
 String value
          A human-readable String containing a reference to the replacement Class, method, or field.
 
Optional Element Summary
 String reason
          The reason the replacement is suggested, in case it's not obvious.
 

Element Detail

value

public abstract String value
A human-readable String containing a reference to the replacement Class, method, or field. It is suggested that you follow the "@see" javadoc semantics for specifying a reference.

reason

public abstract String reason
The reason the replacement is suggested, in case it's not obvious.

Default:
""
